item.title: About
item.description: Who am I? My name is Mitchell. I’m a junior software engineer from the Netherlands with an interest in systems-programming, writing tools and scripts, and Artificial Intelligence. In my short career I’ve already accumulated some experiences with alot of programming languages. Most notably I use Rust, Go, C# and Python almost daily. These 4 are by far my favourite languages. I’ve also racked up some experience with C, C++, Java, Haskell, Bash, web-languages like PHP (& Laravel) & Java/Typescript.
